The Municipal Accountant and Bids and Awards Committee (BAC) submit the required documents to the Office of the Auditor for further evaluation of the transactions pursuant to Section 4(6) of Presidential Decree No. 1445 and GPPB Circular No. 01-2020 dated April 6, 2020;
